### ============================================================
### MANAGEMENT / PROFORMAS
### ============================================================

### List Proformas
GET {{base_api_url}}/management/proformas
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### List Proformas (paginated + search)
GET {{base_api_url}}/management/proformas?page=1&per_page=10&search=FP
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Proforma
GET {{base_api_url}}/management/proformas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create Proforma
POST {{base_api_url}}/management/proformas
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "due_date": "2026-04-15",
  "billing_name": "Jan Kowalski",
  "address": "ul. Szkolna 15",
  "city": "Warszawa",
  "country": "PL",
  "services": [
    {
      "service_id": 1,
      "quantity": 1,
      "discount": 0
    },
    {
      "service_id": 2,
      "quantity": 2,
      "discount": 10.00
    }
  ]
}

### Update Proforma
PUT {{base_api_url}}/management/proformas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "billing_name": "Jan Kowalski - Updated",
  "due_date": "2026-05-01",
  "services": [
    {
      "service_id": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "discount": 5.00
    }
  ]
}

### Delete Proforma (soft delete)
DELETE {{base_api_url}}/management/proformas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Restore Proforma
POST {{base_api_url}}/management/proformas/1/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Confirm Proforma (convert to invoice)
POST {{base_api_url}}/management/proformas/1/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
